Chrysler Corp said its ChryslerFirst Inc acquired a major portion of the commercial lendingportfolio of Beneficial Business Credit Corp, a subsidiary ofBeneficial Corp.    It said the acquisition involves about 84 mln dlrs of netreceivables.    Chrysler First, a subsidiary of Chrysler Financial Corp,had receivables of 4.3 billion dlrs at the end of 1986. Reuter&#3;